OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,FDonald Trump has warned Iran against
OL,7,Fany plans to assassinate him, telling
OL,8,FTehran that the US army would
OL,9,F"completely decimate and destroy all
OL,10,Fareas" of the country in retaliation.
OL,12,FHis comments come after the funeral of
OL,13,FIran's late supreme leader Ayatollah
OL,14,FAli Khamenei saw open calls for Mr
OL,15,FTrump's death.
