OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,FIn a post on Truth Social early on
OL,7,FSaturday, Mr Trump wrote: "1000
OL,8,FMissiles are Locked and Loaded and
OL,9,Faimed at the Islamic Republic of Iran,
OL,10,Fwith thousands of more to immediately
OL,11,Ffollow, should the Iranian Government
OL,12,Fact on its threat, pronounced in many
OL,13,Fcorners of the Globe, to assassinate,
OL,14,For attempt to assassinate, the sitting
OL,15,FPresident of the United States of
OL,16,FAmerica, in this case, ME!
