OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,F"Orders have already been given, and
OL,7,Fthe U.S. Military is ready, willing,
OL,8,Fand able, for a one year period of
OL,9,Ftime, subject to extension, to
OL,10,Fcompletely decimate and destroy all
OL,11,Fareas of Iran ` PRAISE BE TO ALLAH!
OL,12,FPresident DONALD J. TRUMP."
OL,14,FThe US earlier demanded that Iran
OL,15,Fpublicly state the Strait of Hormuz is
OL,16,Fopen and that ships using the vital
OL,17,Fwaterway will not be attacked.
