OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,FBut just as Washington was seeking
OL,7,Fpublic guarantees over the strait,
OL,8,FTehran's top diplomat at the United
OL,9,FNations insisted any activity in the
OL,10,FGulf channel "rests exclusively with
OL,11,FIran".
OL,13,FEnding Tehran's stranglehold on the
OL,14,Fsea route, which disrupted global oil
OL,15,Fand gas supplies and drove up fuel and
OL,16,Ffood prices, had been a key demand in
OL,17,Fprevious negotiations.
OL,26,@rD@NOUsD@EO]
