OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,FHowever, the initial deal reached
OL,7,Fbetween the US and Iran only provides
OL,8,Ffor safe, toll-free passage of the
OL,9,Fwaterway for 60 days, pending the
OL,10,Foutcome of a final agreement on
OL,11,FTehran's disputed nuclear plans.
OL,13,FThe pact also leaves it to Iran and
OL,14,FOman, in conjunction with other Gulf
OL,15,Fstates, to "define the future
OL,16,Fadministration and maritime services
OL,17,Fin the Strait of Hormuz".
OL,26,@wD@LOUyD@XO]
