OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,FIn the meantime, Iran has continued to
OL,7,Ftry to exert leverage over the
OL,8,Fchannel, including demanding ships
OL,9,Fseek permission to transit and raising
OL,10,Fthe spectre of future charges.
OL,12,FIran's ambassador to the UN, Amir
OL,13,FSaeid Iravani said on Friday: "Any
OL,14,Fattempt, by external actors, to
OL,15,Finterfere with or establish a power
OL,16,Farrangement would violate the (interim
OL,17,Fdeal), and undermine its
OL,18,Fimplementation, delay the restoration
OL,19,Fof normal commercial navigation,
OL,20,Fjeopardise maritime safety, and
OL,21,Fincrease regional tensions."
