OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the US military has been
OL,7,Fworking to counter claims by Iran that
OL,8,Fit controls the sea route and that
OL,9,Ftransit is only permitted through its
OL,10,Fapproved designated routes.
OL,12,FNevertheless, shipping using the
OL,13,Fchannel has plummeted following the
OL,14,Frecent fighting, with traffic already
OL,15,Fwell down compared to before the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
