OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,FEarlier in the week, the US president
OL,7,Fbranded the Tehran leadership "scum"
OL,8,Fand said it was "a waste of time"
OL,9,Fdealing with the regime, amid
OL,10,Fexchanges of fire after Iran targeted
OL,11,Fthree tankers in the strait, which has
OL,12,Fremained a flashpoint.
OL,14,FIn a post on his Truth Social platform
OL,15,Fon Friday, Mr Trump said: "The Islamic
OL,16,FRepublic of Iran has asked us to
OL,17,Fcontinue 'talks'.
