OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,F"We have agreed to do so, but the
OL,7,FUnited States has stated to them, in
OL,8,Fno uncertain terms, that the Cease
OL,9,FFire is OVER!"
OL,11,FThe trading of strikes has again
OL,12,Fcaused severe disruption to maritime
OL,13,Ftraffic in the critical sea route,
OL,14,Fcasting doubt on securing a permanent
OL,15,Fend to the conflict, launched by the
OL,16,FUS and Israel on February 28.
OL,18,FMr Trump has also suggested the US
OL,19,Fcould reimpose its blockade of Iranian
OL,20,Fports, having already pulled Tehran's
OL,21,Flicence to sell oil.
