OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,FIn a further retaliatory move, the US
OL,7,FTreasury acted to crack down on a key
OL,8,Ffinancier to the Tehran regime, Dubai-
OL,9,Fbased banker and businessman Ali
OL,10,FAnsari, previously sanctioned by
OL,11,FBritain for his role in financially
OL,12,Fsupporting the activities of Iran's
OL,13,FIslamic Revolutionary Guard Corps
OL,14,F(IRGC).
OL,16,FBefore the latest flare-up,
OL,17,Fnegotiations between the two sides had
OL,18,Fbeen due to restart following the
OL,19,Fburial of Ayatollah Khamenei, who was
OL,20,Fkilled on the first day of the
OL,21,Fconflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
