OL,3,CDonald Trump warns Iran against
OL,4,Cpursuing any assassination attempt
OL,6,FMediators are engaged in frantic
OL,7,Fdiplomatic efforts to try and salvage
OL,8,Fthe tattered peace process.
OL,10,FAt the same time, Israel has said it
OL,11,Fstands ready to confront Iran again if
OL,12,Fneeded.
OL,14,FThe country's defence minister Israel
OL,15,FKatz said: "If we will have to return,
OL,16,Fwe will return with even greater
OL,17,Fforce."
